Is WOLAND free?

WOLAND is freely-avaialble to non-profit use, including research and academic users, under a GNU license. For commercial use please contact author at <tiagoantonio@gmail.com>.

Where can I get help?

If you are having issues, please let us know. We have a mailing list located at: <woland@google-groups.com>.
